title: Quarkus 2.9.2.Final released - Maintenance release
content: Today, we released Quarkus 2.9.2.Final, our second maintenance release for 2.9. It comes with a bunch of fixes and documentation improvements. It is a safe upgrade for anyone already using 2.9 and is highly recommended. If you are not using 2.9 already, please refer to the 2.9 migration guide. Full...
